OL,3,CMan who set girlfriend on fire guilty
OL,4,Cof murder
OL,6,FA man whose girlfriend died two years
OL,7,Fafter he set her on fire has pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to her murder.
OL,10,FLeigh Pateman doused 42-year-old Ellen
OL,11,FMarshall in petrol as she sat in a
OL,12,Fchair before setting her alight at
OL,13,FFirbeck Avenue, Skegness, during an
OL,14,Fargument in April 2021.
OL,16,FPateman, 45, was jailed in March 2022
OL,17,Ffor 17 years and 10 months after
OL,18,Fadmitting a charge of causing grievous
OL,19,Fbodily harm with intent.
