OL,3,CMan who set girlfriend on fire guilty
OL,4,Cof murder
OL,6,FBut he was charged with murder after
OL,7,FMs Marshall died aged 43 in Nottingham
OL,8,FCity Hospital on 11 March 2023 -
OL,9,Fnearly two years after the attack.
OL,11,FPateman admitted the charge when he
OL,12,Fappeared at Lincoln Crown Court via
OL,13,Fvideo link from HMP Garth on Friday.
OL,15,FJudge Simon Hirst adjourned sentencing
OL,16,Funtil 2 December, telling him: "You
OL,17,Fknow the only sentence I can pass upon
OL,18,Fyou is one of life imprisonment.
