OL,3,CMan who set girlfriend on fire guilty
OL,4,Cof murder
OL,6,F"What I need to decide is the mininum
OL,7,Fterm you will have to serve before you
OL,8,Fcan appear before a parole board."
OL,10,FA court previously heard Pateman had
OL,11,Fmade threats to set Ms Marshall on
OL,12,Ffire before the fatal attack.
OL,14,FFollowing the incident Ms Marshall,
OL,15,Fwho was originally from Nottingham,
OL,16,Fwas found lying on the floor of the
OL,17,Fproperty by firefighters.
OL,19,FShe was still conscious and managed to
OL,20,Fgive her name, but claimed the
OL,21,Finjuries were self-inflicted.
