OL,4,Cof murder
OL,6,FShe had suffered 80% burns and was
OL,7,Ftaken to Nottingham City Hospital,
OL,8,Fbefore being transferred to a
OL,9,Fspecialist burns unit.
OL,11,FDespite 12 hours of surgery she was
OL,12,Fgiven less than a 50% chance of
OL,13,Fsurvival.
OL,15,FPateman, who had fled the scene on his
OL,16,Fbike, was found at his mother's house,
OL,17,Fwhere he had gone to bed, covered in
OL,18,Fsoot.
OL,20,FHe was arrested and treated for burns
OL,21,Fbefore being taken into police custody.
