OL,3,CMan who set girlfriend on fire guilty
OL,4,Cof murder
OL,6,FDet Insp Andy McWatt, of Lincolnshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "This was a truly
OL,8,Fshocking and barbaric attack. I cannot
OL,9,Fbegin to imagine how much fear she
OL,10,Fmust have felt, and how painful the
OL,11,Frest of Ellen's life was.
OL,13,F"Her family had to watch someone they
OL,14,Flove suffer from terrible injuries for
OL,15,Falmost two years. I hope that they can
OL,16,Ffeel some measure of closure that her
OL,17,Fkiller will now be sentenced for that
OL,18,Fcrime."
